---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../ui/SectionHeading.astro';
import { pricingConfig, formatCAD } from '../../config/pricing';
import { siteConfig } from '../../config/site';
---

<Section bg="surface" id="practice-pricing">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeading tag="h2" size="2xl">
        Running a practice with five or more physicians?
      </SectionHeading>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-muted font-body">
        One account, one invoice, every physician on the platform. The practice tier gives you 10% off the standard per-physician rate, with annual billing adding a further 5% for a total of up to 15% off list price.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse text-left" role="table">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b-2 border-primary/10">
              <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-display text-sm font-bold text-primary" scope="col">&nbsp;</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 font-display text-sm font-bold text-primary" scope="col">Per physician, monthly</th>
              <th class="py-3 pl-4 font-display text-sm font-bold text-primary" scope="col">Per physician, annually</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-primary/5">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-body font-medium text-text">
                Practice tier ({pricingConfig.practice.minimumPhysicians}+ physicians)
              </td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-body text-text">
                {formatCAD(pricingConfig.practice.monthlyRate)}/month <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">({pricingConfig.practice.clinicDiscountPercent}% off)</span>
              </td>
              <td class="py-4 pl-4 font-body text-text">
                {formatCAD(pricingConfig.practice.annualRate)}/year <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">(~{formatCAD(Math.round(pricingConfig.practice.annualRate / 12))}/month, ~{pricingConfig.practice.maxDiscountPercent}% off)</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-text font-body">
        <p>
          Every physician on the practice account gets the full platform: their own dashboard, their own rules engine and advice engine, their own claims data. The practice administrator manages seats and receives a single consolidated invoice, but does not have access to individual physician billing data or claim details. Your billing performance is your own.
        </p>
        <p>
          Physicians can be added at any time, prorated to your billing cycle. If a physician leaves, they're removed at the end of the current calendar month. If the practice drops below five physicians, each remaining subscription reverts to the standard individual rate.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
          Plus {pricingConfig.gstPercent}% GST. Same features, same support, same continuous updates as individual subscriptions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href={siteConfig.ctaUrl}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-accent px-6 py-3 text-base font-body font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent"
        >
          Get started with practice pricing
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
